{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a bustling harbor scene dominated by a large bridge and shipping infrastructure. The bridge, a towering steel structure with suspension cables, spans the horizon and serves as a prominent backdrop. Beneath the bridge, a busy port area is visible, filled with stacks of colorful shipping containers, indicating a hub for international trade. Large cranes are positioned along the shoreline, actively loading and unloading cargo from ships. The water is calm, reflecting the sky and creating a mirrored effect. In the distance, faint hills or mountains are visible, adding depth to the landscape. A flock of birds flies above, further emphasizing the vastness of the scene. The overall impression is one of industrial activity and global commerce.",
